{"tid":1526921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"趁住今日BTS有條友生日，我地應該再推爆呢張相，連同琴日831件事推上國際","createTime":"2019-09-01T08:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T15:38:09.000Z","uid":161902,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec8699f9dcfa54eaf0eab4046c21525dd5651cd","tid":1526921,"uid":161902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"琴日Twitter發現大部分trending tag都係圍繞住BTS個個征槶。原來係佢生日。<br />\n<br />\n之前有人影到有隻BT21嘅兔仔公仔係所有野結束之後，被遺留低。相信係混亂間跌咗落地下。而咁啱佢就係征槶設計嘅角色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFOdVx2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFOdVx2.jpg&h=eaed9d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以BTS嘅影響力同埋佢地嘅粉絲群，同埋依家個趁住設計呢隻兔仔嘅征槶生日。<br />\n<br />\n我地應該係Twitter 再一次推呢張相，連同琴日831班狗無差別打人一齊推（因為當中被打嘅有可能有bts粉絲，我諗征槶/bts都唔想見到自己嘅粉絲受傷被打）再用埋佢地已經推好晒嘅tag，黎個順水推舟，將琴日班狗做過嘅野再推上國際層面！<br />\n<br />\n會推嘅，記住加呢幾個tag！<br />\n<br />\n#JUNGKOOK <br />\n#HappyBirthdayJungkook <br />\n#JUNGKOOKBIRTHDAY2019 <br />\n#BTS<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n<br />\n光復香港、時代革命。<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"13909c1186b26366601b93dc37a0a1180cbb1017","tid":1526921,"uid":161902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4b1c48e9b6a4f24a69b67d31d9c4cf12db3a56","tid":1526921,"uid":161902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"792508882fa691313e43abd068e982d74ecdb40f","tid":1526921,"uid":161902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"26e9c2cc1af7510738b3a66ccf560ef460b9b8e3","tid":1526921,"uid":302911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:09:31.000Z","msg":"就算P，都推<br />\n係fanclub到推爆